{"type":"message","id":"059b82c0","parentId":"165a43ee","timestamp":"2026-03-19T10:29:50.715Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why fetching the declaration list failed. Let me look at the error details.\n\nThe key error is: \"未匹配到符合条件的报文\" - this means the API was called successfully (authentication worked), but the returned data didn't match expected conditions.\n\nThis could be a sandbox issue - the test company (智谱模型-Agent-沙箱测试税号5) might not have any declaration data set up for 2026-03, or the sandbox environment might have limited test data.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"从日志来看，API 调用本身是成功的（鉴权通过），问题出在返回的数据上：\n\n**\"未匹配到符合条件的报文\"** — 说明企享云的接口有返回数据，但系统没有从中匹配到符合本期（2026年3月）申报条件的记录。\n\n可能的原因：\n\n1. **沙箱测试企业本期没有需要申报的税种** — 这个测试税号在沙箱里可能没有配置2026年3月的应申报数据\n2. **沙箱环境的清册数据未生成** — 沙箱可能需要手动触发或预置清册数据才能拉到\n3. **期次问题** — 当前是3月19日，部分税种的申报期可能还没到，清册尚未生成\n\n要排查的话，可以先确认：这个沙箱测试税号5在企享云后台是否已经存在3月的申报数据/清册？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":702,"output":399,"cacheRead":18699,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19800,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773916182629}}
